Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.47,0:15:08.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}可是葉月最近總是說起美世小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}旭はそれが気に入らなかったようです
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}旭可能因此鬧情緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}まさかそれが　こんなことにつながるとは
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.11,0:15:17.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}沒想到他會做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}美世ちゃんに嫉妬してたのよね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}你在嫉妒美世啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.15,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}おばかさんね
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}小傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}私はこんなに旭のことが好きなのに
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}我明明這麼喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}{\bord1.25}じゃあ　美世さんと僕　どっちが好きなの?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}{\bord1.25}那美世小姐和我，你更喜歡誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}旭はお父さんが好き?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你喜歡爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}好き
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.58,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}私のことは?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}那喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}大好き
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.01,0:15:39.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}お父さんとお母さん　どっちが好き?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.38,0:15:42.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}那爸爸和媽媽，你更喜歡誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}私　旭のことはもちろん特別に大好きよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}我當然非常喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:54.35,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}でも　美世ちゃんのこともとっても大切なの
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.92,0:15:54.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}但美世也是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}旭も美世ちゃんも　大事な家族だもの
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}你和美世，都是重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.20,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}美世さんも家族なの?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}美世也是家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.28,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}ええ　そうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}嗯，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:08.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}旭と私は離れて暮らしているけど　家族でしょ?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.29,0:16:08.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.25}{\3c&1A2B40\4c&1A2B40}我們沒有住在一起，不也是家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}美世ちゃんも血はつながってないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}美世雖然和我沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}私の自慢の妹なの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}但也是令我驕傲的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.01,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}葉月さんも…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&36454F\4c&36454F}葉月小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}私の…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}私の自慢のお姉さんです
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}也是令我驕傲的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}そう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.06,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}そう　そうなのよ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.06,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}對，說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:37.24,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}いきなり言われるとこう　来るものがあるわね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.06,0:16:37.24,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}妳突然這麼說，我好感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}だからね　旭
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}聽好了，旭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}美世ちゃんにも優しくしてあげて
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}以後要好好對待美世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}あの…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&3B5669\4c&3B5669}那個…
