Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}你來這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}怒らないでください
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.94,0:18:41.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5}請不要生氣
